functions.name: operator<<
functions.logic: Overloads the << operator to print a human-readable string representation of the MaybeRegisterRepresentation enum. It uses a switch statement to determine which string to output based on the value of the 'rep' parameter.

functions.name: operator<<
functions.logic: Overloads the << operator to print a human-readable string representation of the MemoryRepresentation enum. It uses a switch statement to determine which string to output based on the value of the 'rep' parameter.
